      <p>Nos plombiers qualifiés interviennent en 30 minutes chrono sur Namur, Jambes, Erpent et alentours 24h/24 et 7j/7.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="emergency-cta">
      <a href="tel:081394820" class="btn btn-emergency">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>
        Appel Direct: 081 39 48 20
      </a>
      <span class="sub-text">⚡ Devis gratuit immédiat & sans engagement</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .emergency-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.12) 0%, rgba(15, 28, 48, 0.95) 100%);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
    padding: 3rem 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .emergency-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .emergency-content {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .emergency-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin: 0.8rem 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .emergency-content p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .emergency-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .sub-text {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .emergency-container {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .emergency-content {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
